Do you have Nvidia GPU and GPU drivers installed?

No, i use dual graphics. An Intel and an AMD. And yes, i have my drivers installed and updated.
I'll try with another driver and see what happens

If you don't use Nvidia GPU then you can't use waifu2x-caffe since it's based on CUDA and CUDNN.
You'll have to use waifu2x-converter-cpp.

Okay, it worked! It took several hours, but i'm happy with the result

Thanks again. Keep it up!
